d52af95542f155087b511c120","tid":2392591,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:13:24.000Z","msg":"《盈利預喜》藥明生物(<a href=\"http://02269.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02269.HK&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5df62434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02269.HK</a>)料年度純利按年增逾65%<br />\n更新日期： 2021年1月27日週三 下午5:42&middot;1 分鐘文章<br />\n<br />\n藥明生物(<a href=\"http://02269.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02269.HK&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5df62434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02269.HK</a>)發盈喜，預期截至去年12月31日止年度的純利按年增長65%以上。 公司指，這主要是由於集團贏得新綜合項目顯著更高市場份額；成功推出「贏得藥物分子」戰略，從而在研發管線中引入更多後期項目並提高近期收益；於去年下半年加速高效推進更多COVID-19項目；多個技術平台產生的里程碑收益強勁增長；現有產能利用率的持續提升帶來更高的運營效率和毛利率；持有的上市及未上市投資組合的公允價值變動推高投資收益；以及外匯風險管理及戰略有效降低預計匯兌損失等原因所致。"},{"pid":"b717ef5c9d627eb861423f8214466921e143e8e3","tid":2392591,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6e5bd2daf59611f835f4ac0c11697d9f69fab93","tid":2392591,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195b81c73411d91e7d9ab82b081d6d645f40216f","tid":2392591,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"又有買入機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"跌少少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"咁等110<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實到"},{"pid":"0ff02862c039df5c66b9f0a8d8a41a9a50fd583d","tid":2392591,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"不斷抽水仲有ON鳩仔科水睇好，支那養豬真係話都冇咁易，大把豬送上門比佢插條供血喉係條頸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f